text: The 1958-59 Austrian Cup was Austria's nationwide football cup competition. FK Austria Wien were the defending champions from the 1948-49 season. From 1949-50 till 1957-58 no Cup competition was held.Austria soccer.at == Round of 32 == *First round with teams from Staatsliga A and Staatsliga B. == Round of 16 == == Quarter-finals == ==Semi-finals == == Final == *Wiener AC: Franz Pelikan - Herbert Brtnicky-Janecek - Karl Kowanz - Viktor Mach - Herbert Lenzinger - Bohumil Hruska - Rudolf Schrötter - Stefan Szokol - Ernst Kaltenbrunner - Norbert Schilling - Kurt Reiter coach: Johann Kliwitsch *SK Rapid Wien: Walter Zeman - Wilhelm Zaglitsch - Walter Glechner - Josef Höltl - Gerhard Hanappi - Karl Gießer - Paul Halla - Rudolf Flögel- Alfred Körner - Josef Bertalan coach: Robert Körner == References == == Other websites == * Category:Austrian Cup Category:1950s in Austria
